      "id": 806191,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "## Summary\n\nA vulnerability in HEY's inbound email processing could allow crafted emails to bypass spam filtering and The Screener when they appear to be in reply to an existing thread.\n\n## Impact\n\nAn attacker who obtained a valid Message-ID from a target's mailbox could send emails that bypassed HEY's spam detection and appeared directly in existing threads, even when the mail server flagged them as spam.\n",
